Show chisquare table

Source: R/show_t_table.R
show_x2_table.Rd

Show chisquare table

Usage

show_x2_table(DF = 1, x2 = NULL, p = 0.05)

Arguments

DF

Numeric degree of freedom

x2

Numeric vector of chi-square value

p

Numeric probability

Value

An object of class "flextable"

Examples

show_x2_table(DF=2,x2=1.5)
